data.description: Honey, stop the car! This is the one… When traditional gem meets southern charm… welcome to 242 White St. NW! This adorable no HOA, ranch style home has it all including character! Situated on a corner lot, you will have an abundance of room to roam and entertain. Plenty of parking with front and rear parking access, do I park in the back or the front, I don’t know, you decide!? And with over 1,500 square feet and an open floor plan, you will feel right at home and cozy! 242 is conveniently located in the heart of Concord with easy access to major roads, shopping, dining, parks, Concord Mills, SEA LIFE, and of course, the speedway! Welcome home to 242 White St. NW!
